  "id": "CHAR_atheron_shale",
  "label": "Atheron Shale",
  "description": "This individual is an undead of the Rift, reduced to a gaunt human frame with taupe skin pulled tight over prominent bone. Gray eyes sit deep in soot-stained sockets, and gray hair persists in uneven clumps along a receded scalp, leaving a skull-like contour plainly visible. The mouth line is split by vitrified cracking at the lips and jaw, a permanent Rift-burn that fixes the face in a rigid, funerary set. They move with rote persistence and exhibit a dulled, compulsive attention to heat, glass, and fracture-lines, as if bound to the site’s ruin by habit rather than will.",
